ht: bold;\">V.I.P. Room</span><br></td><td style=\"text-align: center; \"><span style=\"font-weight: bold; font-family: Arial;\">Common Room</span><br></td></tr><tr><td style=\"text-align: center; \"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">Pachmarhi (1+3 Room)</span><br></td><td style=\"text-align: center; \"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">3000</span><br></td><td style=\"text-align: center; \"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">2000</span><br></td></tr><tr><td style=\"text-align: center; \"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">Mahadev (1+2 Room)</span><br></td><td style=\"text-align: center; \"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">3000</span><br></td><td style=\"text-align: center; \"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">2000</span><br></td></tr><tr><td style=\"text-align: center; \"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">Madhai (2+2 Room)</span><br></td><td style=\"text-align: center; \"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">3000</span><br></td><td style=\"text-align: center; \"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">2000</span><br></td></tr><tr><td style=\"text-align: center; \"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">Churna (2+4 Rooms)</span><br></td><td style=\"text-align: center; \"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">3000</span><br></td><td style=\"text-align: center; \"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">2500</span><br></td></tr></tbody></table></div><h6 style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: bold;\">Room reservation conditions in Forest Rest Houses:-</span></h6><p style=\"text-align: justify; \"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial;\">1. Rooms are reserved in proportion to the fixed number of members. There is an arrangement for the rest of the two people in one room. A maximum of three persons can be allowed to rest in a room. Extra bed facility is not available in the rest houses.<br></span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial;\">2. Rooms are reserved in proportion to the members of the tourists after receiving advance rent for the rooms of the forest rest houses.<br></span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial;\">3. Advance Room Rent by Tourists in the Central Bank of India Branch Pipariya of Deputy Director Satpura Tiger Reserve, Hoshangabad Savings Account No. - 3614151883(IFSC-CBIN0283243) Will be deposited in<br>4. After depositing the fixed amount in the account by the tourist, it will be necessary to scan the statement and send the application details of the reservation along with the application details of the field director, Satpura Tiger Reserve, Hoshangabad office to the e-mail <span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">ddsatnp.hbd@mp.gov.in</span>&nbsp;as soon as possible after depositing the prescribed amount in the account.</span><br><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial;\">5. Tourists, after depositing the amount for room reservation as per the above procedure and sending the deposit slip to this office by e-mail, can get information about their reservation over the phone.<br></span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial;\">6. Due to administrative reasons, the room reservation made by the tourists will be canceled by the Satpura Tiger Reserve Management after giving prior notice. As a result of this, according to the convenience of the concerned tourists, if the room is vacant, they will be given a reservation on the upcoming dates or the advance amount of the room reservation will be returned.</span></p><h6></h6><div style=\"text-align: justify; \"><br></div><p></p>','en_US','publish','2022-07-08 00:58:38','2023-01-31 00:58:57','all',NULL),(26,'Souvenir Shop','souvenir-shop',NULL,NULL,'<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">To Be Filled.....</span></span></h2>','en_US','publish','2022-07-08 00:58:54','2022-07-08 01:21:24','all',NULL),(27,'Points of Interest','points-of-interest',NULL,NULL,'<p styl